%% seq_02_task_crud.mmd
%% Scope: Task interaction overview only.
%% Detail files:
%%   - seq_02a_task_create_update.mmd
%%   - seq_02b_task_status_assignment.mmd
%%   - seq_02c_task_delete.mmd

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant C as Controller
    participant Cmd as Command
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant Evt as Event Bus

    Note over U, Evt: CREATE OR UPDATE TASK
    U->>B: Submit task form
    B->>C: POST/PUT /tasks
    C->>Cmd: CreateTaskCommand or UpdateTaskCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Persist task aggregate
    Cmd->>Evt: Emit task:created or task:updated
    C-->>B: Redirect to task page

    Note over U, Evt: EXECUTE TASK WORKFLOW
    U->>B: Change status or assign assignee
    B->>C: PUT /tasks/:id or /tasks/:id/status
    C->>Cmd: UpdateTaskCommand / UpdateTaskStatusCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Save task state
    Cmd->>Evt: Emit task:assigned or task:status:changed
    C-->>B: Return updated task

    Note over U, Evt: DELETE TASK
    U->>B: Delete task
    B->>C: DELETE /tasks/:id
    C->>Cmd: DeleteTaskCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Soft delete task
    Cmd->>Evt: Emit task:deleted
    C-->>B: Redirect to list
